    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per MRL 2 scoping, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision that the worst-case hemolysis operating condition satisfies RH < 1 relative to the predicate device. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated intended use.",
